---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 536-537
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=The Oratory of the Heart
  - 816
By: Brother Lawrence
---
We may make an oratory of our heart wherein to retire from time to
time to converse with Him in meekness, humility, and love. Every one
is capable of such familiar conversation with God. some more, some
less. He knows what we can do. Let us begin, then.
